se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider.MetadataProvider

Packages that use MetadataProvider
Package
Description
se.swedenconnect.opensaml.saml2.metadata.provider
This library introduces the concept of a "metadata provider" which is a wrapper around a MetadataResolver and allows for easier access to SAML metadata.
